obs-build (2013.05.30-0co1endless10) wheezy; urgency=medium

  * Support control.tar.xz archives in debs. Since dpkg-1.19, the default
    is to xz compress the control archive.
    - d/patches/endless-Handle-.deb-files-that-have-sysv-ar-1-filenames.patch:
      Unneeded, but makes subsequent patches apply correctly.
    - d/patches/endless-deb-Generalize-ungzip-to-uncompress.patch: Allow
      different compression formats.
    - d/patches/endless-Deb.pm-support-control.tar.xz.patch: Use unxz to
      decompress control.tar.xz archives.
    - debian/control: Recommend xz-utils for unxz. This is also needed
      for obs-worker since it receives a copy of obs-build.

 -- Dan Nicholson <nicholson@endlessm.com>  Tue, 09 Jan 2018 12:52:04 -0600

