obs-build (2013.05.30-0co1endless6) wheezy; urgency=medium

  * debian/patches/endless-kill-sigterm.patch: Try to kill chroot
    processes with SIGTERM before SIGKILL to allow them a chance to
    cleanup. This affects faked exhausting the system's IPC semaphores
    when it can't cleanup. (T14181)

